- **Subpath exports** — `"./theme"` follows the exact structure of `"./model"`, `"./git"`, etc. in `packages/shared/package.json`
- **No Effect Schema** — theme definitions are plain constants, no runtime validation needed
- **`.no-transitions` class** — existing flash-prevention mechanism, reused as-is

## Verification

